      <title>套利交易最喜爱的墨西哥比索因中东风险上升而受到打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/carry-trade-favorite-mexican-peso-smacked-by-rising-mideast-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥比索跌幅四年来最大，原因是中东冲突加剧削弱了对墨西哥比索的需求，而墨西哥比索一直是套利交易最喜欢的目标之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/carry-trade-favorite-mexican-peso-smacked-by-rising-mideast-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 05:52:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市因对中东紧张局势和鹰派美联储的担忧而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/asian-stocks-slump-as-mideast-woes-hawkish-fed-sour-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对中东紧张局势升级的担忧以及对美国长期利率上升的担忧，市场普遍出现避险情绪，亚洲股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/asian-stocks-slump-as-mideast-woes-hawkish-fed-sour-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 02:41:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本日经指数因筹码和中东问题下跌超过 3%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/japan-s-nikkei-225-falls-more-than-3-led-lower-by-chip-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国利率前景和中东紧张局势吓坏了投资者，全球股市遭遇抛售，日本日经 225 指数创下 2022 年 6 月以来最大单周跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/japan-s-nikkei-225-falls-more-than-3-led-lower-by-chip-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 01:52:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗媒体淡化以色列的袭击后油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-19</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于伊朗媒体似乎淡化了上周末伊朗空前轰炸后以色列袭击的影响，油价回吐了最初的大幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-19</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 23:23:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票期货因中东担忧而下跌，避风港收益：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲和美国股指期货下跌，因为全球市场受到中东新冲突的冲击，导致股市走低，而石油和包括国债和美元在内的避险资产走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 22:18:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国收紧制裁，俄罗斯石油贸易商涌现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/russia-takes-whack-a-mole-oil-sanctions-dodging-to-a-new-level</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国加大对莫斯科的制裁压力，俄罗斯与印度的原油贸易开始像一场石油打地鼠游戏。正当一位交易员开始失去影响力时，另一位交易员突然出现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/russia-takes-whack-a-mole-oil-sanctions-dodging-to-a-new-level</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 08:50:37 GMT</pubDate>
